name: Santa's Journey '22
description:
Delivering presents to everyone around the globe is no mean feat.
Santa has asked you for help, or he'll be beat!
Gather distance on the ramps you meet, to help Santa on his journey through the sleet.
Once traveled far enough, you may also receive something sweet...

name: Santa's Slalom '23
description:
<center>Santa's Slalom '23</center>
Happy Holidays, everyone! 🎄

As the snow settles and the festive spirit envelops us once more, Santa and his dedicated elves have worked tirelessly to introduce an even more exciting and challenging experience for this holiday season.
